PHP 7+;
JavaScript, HTML, CSS;
MySQL, MongoDB (+);
WordPress (hooks, custom posts/taxonomies/fields, REST API, query creation using wpdb, etc.);
Experience with various CMS platforms (primarily Kernel Video Sharing and WP) as well as frameworks (primarily Laravel);
Experience in writing plugins for WordPress;
Experience in optimizing and securing WordPress;
Strong attention to detail;
Eagerness to work and develop professionally.
